- Baum/Humanware/APH/Orbit
- HumanWare Brailliant BI/B
- HumanWare BrailleNote
- SuperBraille
- Optelec ALVA 6
- HIMS Braille Sense/Braille EDGE/Smart Beetle/Sync Braille
- Eurobraille Esys/Esytime/Iris
